	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Where to begin?
<br />
<br />Using decimal numbers for addresses: horrible idea. no doc will match those, and are a total mess.
<br />
<br />RESET, IRQ, and NMI vectors all point at the same code: Usually, powerup/reset initialization should be done once. This does it every vblank, or would if NMIs were enabled.
<br />
<br />It's confusing to follow, but it looks like it might be trying to update the pallete and nametable during the frame, rather than during retrace, which won't work

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


